      "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/p/ecb155/{size}.png",
      "created_at": "2017-04-18T16:54:00.345Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Me nje fjale, nje hap prapa Turqia. Shumicen e votave ai e morri nga zonat rurale.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Dikur neve s’kishim drita, rruge, Erdogani na i solli te gjitha,- u shpreh nje banor i Turqise lindore.</li>\n</ul>",
